The paper discusses the development of a middleware for secure opportunistic routing schemes in online social networks, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), security (cs.CR), and system design (cs.SI, cs.SY, cs.DC). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.SY, and cs.DC.
